&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and scale a dedicated ML Ops framework that allows Data Scientists to deploy, monitor, and iterate on AI models with industry-leading efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the use of proactive modeling to predict player needs and business

