&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;Gearbox Software is seeking a game designer to join us in developing a first-person shooter. This role involves working in a team environment to design and implement new features and assets. This role will work closely with many departments to iterate and improve the game experience related to non-playable characters (NPCs) specifically.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
