&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Bachelor’s Degree or higher in Computer Science or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 0–3 years of experience (excellent fresh graduates are welcome to apply)&lt;/li&gt;
